MPD plasma client - it small simply plasmoid, written on python, which controls mpd server.
There are only the following functions: previous/next song, play/pause, stop, connect Client connect automatically on localhost:6600

INSTALL:
plasmapkg -i MPD-plasma-client.plasmoid

REMOVE:
plasmapkg -u MPD-plasma-client

NOTE: If you have old version of MPD-plasma-client, remove it, before installing new version
